snippet.title: Sonic: The Murdering Insanity | Gameplay Trailer Debut
snippet.description:
Sonic: The murdering insanity is a Horror RPG game with Sonic.
Game engine - Clickteam Fusion 2.5.
Game template (engine) - Modified Sonic Worlds Delta 1.5.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
What is Sagexpo - This is the place where people show their sonic fan games where we will show our game too!
Say thanks for making this trailer to Dakuresu.
And animations with a castle at the end to ARTEMGAMESHOW (ARTEM THE DEVELOPER) and Hamster Man for helping to fix some problems with it.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Our discord server - https://discord.gg/Ky5Abxq
Sagexpo Twitter - https://twitter.com/sagexpo
Sagexpo youtube channel - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCB9uB5wbkDnFkA_DsUe28cA
TWITTER - https://twitter.com/TeamKosmosTK
GAMEJOLT - https://team-kosmos.gamejolt.io/

And thanks Hedgefoox for all!!!
